              including Responsive designs. I pride myself on delivering
              high-quality work that exceeds expectations. Feel free to explore
              my portfolio and contact me for any project or collaborations .
              let's bring your ideas to life!
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="imgfoot">
            <div class="imgfootl">
              <h3>M Monir Shokohyan</h3>
              <h3>Graphic designer/Web developer</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="plusminus">
              <div id="plus">+</div>
              <div id="minus">&minus;</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info" id="graphicinfo">
          <div class="graphic">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined"> home_app_logo </span
            ><span class="inftext"> Logo Design</span>
          </div>
